<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com">
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Sans:ital,wght@0,100;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;1,100;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'IBM Plex Sans', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            background: url("https://sac-attendance.azurewebsites.net/static/white.png");
            text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
        }

        .main-container {
            display: -ms-flexbox;
            display: -webkit-box;
            display: flex;
            -ms-flex-align: center;
            -ms-flex-pack: center;
            -webkit-box-align: center;
            align-items: center;
            -webkit-box-pack: center;
            justify-content: center;

            margin-top: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .main {
            width: 80vw;
            box-shadow: rgba(17, 17, 26, 0.05) 0px 4px 16px, rgba(17, 17, 26, 0.05) 0px 8px 32px;
            border-radius: .8rem;
            padding: 2rem 4rem;
            padding-bottom: 4rem
        }

        h1,
        h2,
        h3,
        h4,
        h5,
        h6 {
            font-weight: 500
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }

        .subtitle {
            margin-top: -1.6rem;
            color: grey;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
        }

        small {
            color: grey;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
        
        .receipt-details {
            background: #000c1d url("https://sac-attendance.azurewebsites.net/static/bg-email.png");
            background-size: 120%;
            border-left: solid #ff0000 5px;
            border-radius: 7px;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .receipt-details * {
            color: white;
            -moz-user-select: -moz-none;
            -khtml-user-select: none;
            -webkit-user-select: none;
         
            /*
              Introduced in IE 10.
              See http://ie.microsoft.com/testdrive/HTML5/msUserSelect/
            */
            -ms-user-select: none;
            user-select: none;
        }

        .makerspace-mark {
            opacity: .15;
            height: 2rem;
        }

        hr {
            border: none;
            border-top: 2px solid rgb(228, 228, 228);
        }

        footer {
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="main-container">
        <div class="main">
            <h1>You didn't clock out today...</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Details of your incomplete shift.</p>
            <p>Shift details is as follows—</p>
            <div class="receipt-details">
                <li><b>Name:</b> {{ name }}</li>
                <li><b>Card ID:</b> {{ cardID }}</li>
                <li><b>Record UUID:</b> {{ recordID }}</li>
                <li><b>Clock in:</b> {{ times.clockIn }}</li>
                <li><b>Clock out:</b> <span style="color: #ff0000">(unknown)</span></li>
            </div>
            <br>
            <b><small>➔ Please rectify this issue with a coach as soon as possible.</small></b>
            <p><b>Thank you</b><br>MakerSpaceNYP</p>
            <hr>
            <small>This is an automated email sent from an unmonitored email address, please do not reply.</small>
        </div>
    </div>
    <footer>
        <center>
            <object class="makerspace-mark"
                data="http://sac-attendance.azurewebsites.net/static/makerspace-logo.svg"></object>
        </center>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>